The '''''Errinung'ka''''' was one of the two [[Sh'ner-class planetary assault carrier|
''Sh'ner''-class planetary assault carriers]] that was a part of the [[Keeramak Entourage]] that arrived on [[Bakura/Legends|Bakura]] prior to the [[Battle of Bakura (28 ABY)|battle of Bakura]] in [[28 ABY/Legends|28 ABY]] The vessel would see action in that engagement.

